// This is footer component import React from "react"; import phone from '../Images/call-2-1.svg' import mail from '../Images/envelope-01.svg' import mark from '../Images/map.svg' import logo from '../Images/Final-logo-alpha.png' import {phoneNumber} from "../globalVars" import {email} from "../globalVars" import {address} from "../globalVars" import {addressDirection} from "../globalVars"; import "./Footer.css" const Footer = () => { document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() { const numberLink = document.getElementById("phone-number"); numberLink.setAttribute("href", "tel:" + phoneNumber); var emailLink = document.getElementById("email-address"); emailLink.setAttribute("href", "mailto:" + email); var addressLink = document.getElementById("address-direction"); addressLink.setAttribute("href", addressDirection); }); return
